1. *Majmuna* u zoološkom vrtu uvek najviše vole deca. (The *monkey* in the zoo are always loved most by children.)
2. Videla sam *majmune* kako se igraju na drvetu. (*Monkeys* playing on the tree are what I saw.)
3. Mama mi je kupila plišanog *majmuna*. (My mom bought me a plush *monkey*.)
4. Opet si se ponašao kao pravi *majmun* na zabavi sinoć. (You behaved like a real *monkey* at the party last night again.)
5. Sreli smo *majmuna* dok smo šetali kroz džunglu. (We encountered a *monkey* while walking through the jungle.)
6. Moramo biti oprezni kada hranimo *majmune* u parku. (We have to be careful when feeding *monkeys* in the park.)
7. *Majmuni* su veoma inteligentne životinje koje mogu da nauče mnoge stvari. (*Monkeys* are very intelligent animals that can learn many things.)
8. Ljudi često koriste izraz "neka ti *majmuni* skaču po glavi" kada su ljuti na nekoga. (People often use the phrase "let the *monkeys* jump on your head" when they're angry with someone.)